mydlp
An open source data loss prevention solution.

References:
http://www.mydlp.org

Dependencies:
Thrift, Python 2.6, python-magic, unrar, catdoc, pstotext, poppler-utils, python-beautifulsoup, sun-java6-jre

Squid configuration for ICAP:

 icap_enable on
 icap_service service_req reqmod_precache 0 icap://127.0.0.1:1344/request
 icap_class class_req service_req
 icap_access class_req allow all
 icap_send_client_ip on
 icap_preview_enable off

Also request-reply body-header limits for Squid should be edited for requirements.

